Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老師都嚇得夠嗆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深谷!你怎麼提前吃起午飯的便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在才剛第一節課
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽向 你被發那麼大的火也不覺得可怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?對我發火的是美笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是運動部那些傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了多少次把腳上的泥抖掉再進校舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起來!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 魔鬼在與地獄進行通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:08.63,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,18)\bord4\1c&H2F4F4F&\3c&HFFFFFF&}男生們的想像圖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:15.28,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,18)\bord4\1c&H2F4F4F&\3c&HFFFFFF&}經過陽向的視覺濾鏡後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 幹這活還真夠累的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:16.74,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}快逃!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 現在被魔鬼抓到的話 全都會被帶到地獄去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我們吧 為什麼偏偏會喜歡上會長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說過去還不錯 可是現在可是那個樣子啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞男生在哪...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:33.21,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,294)\bord4\1c&H2F4F4F&\3c&HFFFFFF&}(男生對會長的印象)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 確實覺得說話的方式和以前有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是美笑很溫柔的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.87,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}麵包耳朵沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?這麼說來她果然對我有特殊對待?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大M?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大M嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 美笑就是美笑 我的心意不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽向...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:04:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就明白對我來說非美笑不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿成那個樣子幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新校服會髒掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 陽向 撅著嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!陽君快點下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中感覺怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班裡的人數突然多了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能多交幾個朋友就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過得好快啊 這就上初中了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一轉眼長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來這裡的時候 每天都為他擔心得不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛來的時候明明胖嘟嘟地 可是一天天地瘦下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為總吃這些蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說了陽向 給你做肉吃你不是也沒吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候總說沒事 可還是沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算能放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊 跑壘跑壘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,safe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑得更快了啊 明明身上就沒什麼肌肉的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明有練肌肉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無防備 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.78,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,20)\bord4\1c&H2F4F4F&\3c&HFFFFFF&}就\N連\N來\N打\N練\N習\N賽\N的\N對\N方\N學\N校\N的\N學\N生\N都\N.\N.\N.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼 陽向很有人氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他畢竟是王牌嘛 當然會有人氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這麼傻的傢伙 真讓人嫉妒啊這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我 卻沒覺得...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 今天是情人節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保重哦 陽君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?U×misi的演唱會?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 U×misi要在夢笑高中的文化祭上演出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了以前他們的那種可恨的態度了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 好好說說她吧 美笑同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那之後變了哦 空我君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說櫻本打算最後聽一次他們的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可演唱會上空我卻受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻去探病的時候他的態度變了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:08.14,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,10)\bord2\1c&660033&\3c&FFCCCC&}有好多話想說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的變了 所以想讓美笑和靜子也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?碓冰?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢笑高中的文化祭我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你也要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.77,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶他去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是擔心美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑同學 臉很紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和啊 美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠~~~理~~~香~~~理~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理香裡普索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理香大人 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑與我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是與我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是與我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會走到一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我來為你們佔卜一下與美笑的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕夏~魯索~拉奧諾~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠~理~ 香魯波那~拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...本來覺得巫女day玩玩占卜應該不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像不怎麼萌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過店長 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理香好像被什麼附了身一樣 玩得很認真哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波魯波~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.18,0:08:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理 香理 惠理 香理 香摩~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出結果了 這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是興奮大魔神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你們空蕩蕩的腦子一樣 什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:09:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不到 這就是全部 也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you們完全沒戲 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是水晶給予的啟示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用說得這麼絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜從某種意義上說就是對人的一種觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑完全不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己的心意都搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑啊 錯了 這裡應該叫misa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫不熟 真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 深谷 你已經變成這裡的常客了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 外邊寫著占卜DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以為我也占卜一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以了 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 主人 請坐到水晶球前邊的椅子上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 和真的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜一下我和美笑的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕夏~魯索~拉奧諾~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠~理~香魯達蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:55.76,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}期待期待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了紙氣球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:09:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙氣球?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和美笑的未來就是癟掉的紙氣球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許什麼都看不到的我們還算好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 請看仔細點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那癟掉的紙氣球還能吹起來嗎 仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀哦呀 還不肯放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是沒看到有破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 只要沒破洞就說明還能吹起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好樂觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再送你一句
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的這份樂觀也許能帶給你危急關頭的大逆轉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大逆轉?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 我也占卜一下吧 和美笑的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到狗 是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就為您占卜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特塔~魯索~拉奧諾~惠~理~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香摩米露~哈!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明顯把眼睛移開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜的結果是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...是啊是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 沒有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水晶裡 能看到水與火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.71,0:11:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 相性非常差
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法走到一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果知道這些還想走到一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要一起挑戰今後將要到來的嚴酷試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?對我們的啟示怎麼沒有說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點彌補都不給嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我們吧 惠理香大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒叫我們出場啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:11:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 美笑 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你在等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才三下君也在這裡晃悠的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許最後關頭有大逆轉在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打出逆轉本壘打的也許就是三下君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我們的相性那麼差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說碓冰 你是那種會被佔卜左右的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑只對我一個人那麼冷淡就是因為相性差嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是因為你是變態宇宙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣叫我也一定是因為我們相性太差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就因為這點事 就打算離開我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的運動部的那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我絕對不會原諒你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就因為這點事 就打算離開我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你 美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深谷?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:52.26,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,40)\frz+40\1c&H32A24DFD&\3c&3333FF&}不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真髒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽君 好好打掃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在掃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是想起來...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 幫大忙了 深谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是嗎 太好了 我好好幹好好幹好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深谷 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒沒 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換下桶裡的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?沒用就換?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...太可愛了 差點魂兒就飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個會不會比較快?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 膠管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拉到出口附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣一捏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 另外一頭沒接好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 用手堵有什麼用 把水龍頭關上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪邊擰是關來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 都說了不要用手堵了 白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對不起 美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼呢 大冷天的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是碓冰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點換衣服要感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說非得玩水的話我倒也不攔著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 喂深谷 你有衣服可換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有運動服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快點換了衣服回家吧 會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去保健室處理下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:18.26,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(245,75)\fad(100,600)\frz-2\bord2\1c&44BB5C&\3c&HFFFFFF&}沒\N有\N可\N換\N的\N衣\N服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了 你也快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等會長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 會把走廊弄濕的 我從外邊繞過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼啊 又不是會看到內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:34.78,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(45,140)\fad(100,600)\bord2\1c&7A96E9&\3c&HFFFFFF&}穿\N著\N貼\N身\N短\N衫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?你怎麼看 那邊臉紅著的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:39.44,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,70)\bord2\1c&6363EE&\3c&HFFFFFF&}剛才已經注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好害羞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不自覺的話也很過分哦 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啊 不至於
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不肯穿的話我就在這裡脫到全裸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不怕我全裸跳到校門前去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 別脫 你這變態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想汪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長也喵一下看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?你到底想幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 可能已經有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的像陽向說的那麼可愛的話就更可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.70,0:17:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果變得又胖又醜的話倒不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算變胖了美笑也絕對很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說來肯定已經有男朋友了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 你果然沒有考慮過啊 太天真了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可馬上就是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在城市的女孩子就算是初中生...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升到高中以後 就連這種事呀那種事都...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭你也看看我在我老姐房間裡找到的書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們玩男人的身體玩到讓人噁心的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑不會做那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定還是個又純真又可愛又善良的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 不要再傷害滿懷夢想的初中男生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不覺得這小子需要正視現實嗎 諸君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 確實有些讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如現在還藏著當初告別時候拿到的糖果包裝紙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你見過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們棒球部為了祈禱勝利買的求勝護符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是把它打開 把那糖果包裝紙放進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的第二輪比賽就是因為你才輸了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊 就是靠我第一輪才贏了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這倒無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說升高中以後要去找她 是認真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你期待過高的話 等著你的可不只是失落哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做好覺悟再去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟有是有...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真夠難受的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等美笑罵我糾纏不休的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候再想該怎麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數日後 天氣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉君~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了很久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是很久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢笑高中的文化祭 據說很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AOI醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的正好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算拍上次沒拍成的湖邊場景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們反正也沒事幹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 拿著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂上賊船容易下賊船難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要幫他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才開始焰火的聲音就很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等噪音消失以後就開始 拜託了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 今年也好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽別人說過 不過沒想到規模居然這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說他們的校風就是喜歡熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說半年前就開始籌備了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:19:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那莫非就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U×misi來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空我君 給你好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你太煩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早說過了 想得到我們的愛 就要做好姑娘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到的小乖貓都跟上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 櫻 靜子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人流帶到了舞台前邊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這人海的對面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這人海 都在搶演唱會的席位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻一步都不想動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要我不要離舞台更遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 我們在演唱會結束前會留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是沒法與你們會合了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑你們先自己玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?我說 靜子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說讓我玩玩...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 空我君最近變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂隊的氣氛也不一樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得給人一種褒義上的緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也覺得和粉絲拉開了一些距離...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒有再聽到以前那種和粉絲不清不白的緋聞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於純粹想享受音樂的粉絲來說是個好消息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實像櫻說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫空我的給人的感覺和以前不大一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信不相信他先另說...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很擔心櫻...很擔心...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 關注的領域不同 思維方式也不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在再怎麼想也沒用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩玩...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然仍然覺得在被碓冰耍的團團轉...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個 就是因為你突然說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好的夢笑祭 兩個人一起去玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次變成撒嬌的語氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太麻煩了 還是看櫻和靜子那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭蟲樂隊的演出還不開始嗎 櫻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.37,0:23:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是U×misi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.37,0:24:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空我君如果會唱新曲的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了會長 是不是宣佈一下下一話是最終話比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 那得做些適合最終回做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看誠實的鯰澤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰是白癡!
